snippet.title: Spectral Prison: Trapped in a Nightmare
snippet.description:
Wishlist today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3260000/Spectral_Prison/
Try the demo now at: https://moonlightreaperhien.itch.io/spectral-prison

Step into a world of terror in Spectral Prison. Wake up trapped in a haunted house filled with chilling surprises. Solve puzzles, find keys, and avoid the terrifying jump scares as you try to escape. But the absolute nightmare begins when the warden catches you. Can you survive the spectral prison?
